stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle: note loaded / cleared
    Idle --> TextOnly: highlight text in Note View
    Idle --> SpanClicked: click Note View span
    Idle --> RowClicked: click Spans row
    TextOnly --> Ready: choose entity type
    SpanClicked --> NeedsEntity: PHI text set, selection active, entity cleared
    NeedsEntity --> Ready: choose entity type
    RowClicked --> Ready: row text + entity populated
    Ready --> Idle: Add / Correct / Reject / Accept
    TextOnly --> Idle: Clear
    NeedsEntity --> Idle: Clear
    RowClicked --> Idle: Clear
    Ready --> Idle: Clear
